        "🇻🇦 <strong>Vulgata:</strong> et plantabo eos super humum suam et non evellam eos ultra de terra sua quam dedi eis dicit Dominus Deus tuus<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ESTUDO LEXICAL:</span></strong> <em>וּנְטַעְתִּים</em> – 'plantá-los-ei' – plantar, estabelecer. <em>יִנָּתְשׁוּ</em> – 'arrancados' – arrancar, desarraigar. <em>אֲשֶׁר</em> – 'que' – que, a qual. <em>נָתַתִּי</em> – 'dei' – dar, conceder.<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
